title: Digital Puppet Masters Tournament Series - 1v1 - Starting Tommorrow 9am

embed.description: This organization will run tournaments for teams and players of all ranks and skill level, with a main focus on League Of Legends in the Oceanic Region.

body:
Just a friendly reminder that the 1v1 tournament is on again tomorrow. Check in between 8am and 9am for your chance to win the $10 prize. 

Last weeks event was won by Gold ranked Morderick who chose Urgot in both games taking down a platium Jayce and Silver Brand.

Be in it to win it.

You will also find this event on the Community section of this website as it has now been approved by Riot.
